** MES(70) ........2.........3.........4.........5.........6.........7
ENTER SEQ# !                                                           01
LABEL NOT PRINT YET                                                    02
ORDER CANCELLED                                                        03
LABEL PRINTED                                                          04
ASN SENT                                                               05
